Agbor Gilbert Ebot aka AGE (a mụrụ Agbor GilbertEbot; 8 Jenụwarị 1983) bụ onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri Cameroon. Ihe ịga nke ọma ya dịka onye na-eme ihe nkiri gụnyere Before Sunrise, The Blues Kingdom, The Land of Shadow, Pink Poison na Far

O lekwasịrị anya na ihe nkiri sinima nke Afrịka, onye guzobere The Cameroon International Film Festival (CAMIFF ) na-ezube ịkwalite Cinema nke Cameroon ma n'ụzọ akụ na ụba ma n'ọdịbendị site na mgbanwe, nghọta na imekọ ihe ọnụ n'etiti ndị na-eme ihe nkiri na mba.
N'oge na-adịbeghị anya, ọ natara Medal of Honor site n'aka Onye isi ala Cameroon Paul Biya.
A mụrụ Gilbert nye nne na nna Cameroon na Naijiria
Nna ya bụ onye Cameroon si Mamfe na Manyu Division ebe nne ya si Cross River steeti na Naịjirịa. Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Government Technical High School (GTHS) na Mamfe.
Agbor Gilbert agaghị ụlọ akwụkwọ teknụzụ ọ bụla maka ihe nkiri
N'afọ 2003, ọ zutere Jeta Amata, Fred Amata, Olu Jacobs na Rita Dominic na Calabar mgbe ha na-ese ihe nkiri
Ọ na-agakarị ebe ahụ ebe a na-ezipụ ya mgbe niile na klas n'ihi enweghị akwụkwọ ma ọ bụ ngwá ọrụ ziri ezi
Oge ọ bụla ọ laghachiri n'ebe ahụ, ọ ga-anọdụ ala ebe ahụ ma nyere aka dịka onye na-enyere aka na mmepụta ihe nkiri, nke ahụ bụkwa otú mmasị ya na ihe nkiri si too.
N'ọnwa Septemba afọ 2017, ọ nọchitere anya ụlọ ọrụ ihe nkiri Cameroon na Heroes in the Struggle Awards na Los Angeles ma o kwuru

Ebdot mere egwu na-ese okwu megide onye na-ede blọgụ na onye na-eme ihe omume LGBT Bandy Kiki, na-ekwu na ''...Ọ bụrụ na m jide gị maka Cameroon, m ga-edina mmadụ n'ike ị dị mma ka mmụọ ọjọọ nke ụmụ nwanyị na-edina nwanyị wee nwee ahụ gị...Enwere m atụmatụ inye gị belle..."
